oda-data-set.name: whole_dataset
oda-data-set.xml-property: select ESA_NAME,ESA_CODE, sum( case when status = 'Certified' then CNT else 0 end ) total_certified, sum( case when status = 'Request_Not_Made' then CNT else 0 end ) total_request_not_made, sum( case when status = 'Pending Certification' then CNT else 0 end ) total_pending_certification, sum(CNT) as total from( select fep.company_name as ESA_NAME, fep.cbs_acct_code as ESA_CODE,er.device_id,(case when node.certification_status is null then 'Request_Not_Made' when lower(node.certification_status) ='pending_certification' then 'Pending Certification' when lower(node.certification_status) ='certified' then 'Certified' end) as Status,1 CNT from enrollment_ref er join node on node.enrollment_ref = er.id join fep_device_mapping fdm on fdm.device_id=er.device_id join front_end_partner fep ON fep.pk = fdm.front_end_partner_fk )a --where status='Certified' group by ESA_NAME,ESA_CODE order by 3 desc

oda-data-set.name: device_distribution_by_cert_status
oda-data-set.xml-property: select count(distinct device_id) as total,status from( select er.device_id,(case when node.certification_status is null then 'Request_Not_Made' when lower(node.certification_status) ='pending_certification' then 'Pending Certification' when lower(node.certification_status) ='certified' then 'Certified' end) as Status from enrollment_ref er join node on node.enrollment_ref = er.id)a where status is not null group by status;

oda-data-set.name: certifiction_trend
oda-data-set.xml-property: select date_trunc('day',create_date) as date_,status,count(status) as total from(select node.create_date,node.certification_status,dte.esa_code,dte.esa_name,d.requested_device_id,(case when node.certification_status is null then 'Request_Not_Made' when lower(node.certification_status) ='pending_certification' then 'Pending Certification' when lower(node.certification_status) ='certified' then 'Certified' end) as Status from device_tag_request_ext dte join device_tag_request d on dte.pk =d.pk join device_type dt on d.device_type_fk=dt.id join node on dt.id=node.device_type)a group by status,date_trunc('day',create_date) order by date_trunc('day',create_date)

oda-data-set.name: activated_devices
oda-data-set.xml-property: select ESA_NAME,ESA_CODE,count(distinct device_id),status from( select fep.company_name as ESA_NAME, fep.cbs_acct_code as ESA_CODE,er.device_id,(case when node.certification_status is null then 'Request_Not_Made' when lower(node.certification_status) ='pending_certification' then 'Pending Certification' when lower(node.certification_status) ='certified' then 'Certified' end) as Status from enrollment_ref er join node on node.enrollment_ref = er.id join fep_device_mapping fdm on fdm.device_id=er.device_id join front_end_partner fep ON fep.pk = fdm.front_end_partner_fk )a where status='Certified' group by ESA_NAME,ESA_CODE,status order by 3 desc

oda-data-set.name: pending_certification
oda-data-set.xml-property: select ESA_NAME,ESA_CODE,count(distinct device_id),status from( select fep.company_name as ESA_NAME, fep.cbs_acct_code as ESA_CODE,er.device_id,(case when node.certification_status is null then 'Request_Not_Made' when lower(node.certification_status) ='pending_certification' then 'Pending Certification' when lower(node.certification_status) ='certified' then 'Certified' end) as Status from enrollment_ref er join node on node.enrollment_ref = er.id join fep_device_mapping fdm on fdm.device_id=er.device_id join front_end_partner fep ON fep.pk = fdm.front_end_partner_fk )a where status='Pending Certification' group by ESA_NAME,ESA_CODE,status order by 3 desc

oda-data-set.name: request_not_made
oda-data-set.xml-property: select ESA_NAME,ESA_CODE,count(distinct device_id),status from( select fep.company_name as ESA_NAME, fep.cbs_acct_code as ESA_CODE,er.device_id,(case when node.certification_status is null then 'Request_Not_Made' when lower(node.certification_status) ='pending_certification' then 'Pending Certification' when lower(node.certification_status) ='certified' then 'Certified' end) as Status from enrollment_ref er join node on node.enrollment_ref = er.id join fep_device_mapping fdm on fdm.device_id=er.device_id join front_end_partner fep ON fep.pk = fdm.front_end_partner_fk )a where status='Request_Not_Made' group by ESA_NAME,ESA_CODE,status order by 3 desc
